data.description: LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION!! Come check out this beautiful Belmont-Cragin single family home. Conveniently located to Home Depot, Starbucks, Walmart, Aldi, Chase, and other local restaurants. Sellers have lived in this home for 30 + years. This home has 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, 1 half bathroom, finished basement, 2 back porches, a deck, a double door garage (perfect for entertaining), and an extra lot! The owner also has the cutest garden where she grows her own vegetables. Make an offer!
